Title: 14.2 Loadable Function Reference
Name: version_tokens_show()
Description:
Returns the server's list of version tokens as a binary
              string containing a semicolon-separated list of
              name=value
              pairs.

Press CTRL+C to copy mysql> SELECT version_tokens_show();
+--------------------------+
| version_tokens_show()    |
+--------------------------+
| tok2=value2;tok1=value1; |
+--------------------------+
